properties.name: Movie Tavern At Central Park
properties.description: Posted by Redwarlock  2404 Airport Freeway, Suite 100, Bedford, TXThe Central Park Movie Tavern follows in the tradition of Beer, Pizza, and Movies and expands the concept to include a Full Menu, Full Bar, and Full Service. How it works... Purchase your tickets at the box office. We recommend you arrive up to 30 minutes before the start-time of the movie. Once you make your way inside, you will be greeted by our friendly staff who will provide you with a menu and direct you to your theater. Once you have found a seat, your server will bring you a glow coaster. You can press the button on the side anytime you need to summon your server. Your order will be taken, the movie will start, and your food will be delivered to you while you watch the movie. Your bill will be settled towards the end of the film.
